name: Mayans M.C.
overview: Set in the aftermath of Jax Teller’s death, Ezekiel "EZ" Reyes is fresh out of prison and a prospect in the Mayans M.C. charter on the Cali/Mexi border. Now, EZ must carve out his new identity in a town where he was once the golden boy with the American Dream in his grasp.
tagline: Time to choose between club or family.

episodes.name: Perro/Oc
episodes.overview: EZ’s fate is in flux as the M.C. and the cartel find a common adversary.

episodes.name: Escorpión/Dzec
episodes.overview: The Mayans seek answers from a local crew as the Galindo worlds north and south of the border collide.

episodes.name: Búho/Muwan
episodes.overview: The M.C. alliances are tested and the Galindo family adopts unconventional methods.

episodes.name: Murciélago/Zotz
episodes.overview: A new threat in Santo Padre presents the Mayans new obstacles and opportunities.

episodes.name: Uch/Opossum
episodes.overview: A new deal requires a dangerous favor in Santa Madre.

episodes.name: Gato/Mis
episodes.overview: EZ continues to prove his worth as a prospect, as both sides of the border must grapple with harsh realities.

episodes.name: Cucaracha/K'uruch
episodes.overview: New secrets are brought to light, putting the M.C. at odds.

episodes.name: Rata/Ch’o
episodes.overview: EZ’s past continues to haunt him, but present horrors give him a new perspective.

episodes.name: Serpiente/Chikchan
episodes.overview: The bond of the Reyes blood is fractured, and the Galindo family decides to cut their losses.

episodes.name: Cuervo/Tz'ikb'uul
episodes.overview: The club has reason to celebrate, but big changes leave the future uncertain.

episodes.name: Xbalanque
episodes.overview: The Reyes family is divided and the M.C. uncovers an internal leak.

episodes.name: Xaman-Ek
episodes.overview: As EZ and Angel reconnect, complications arise for the M.C. and Galindo.

episodes.name: Camazotz
episodes.overview: Mayans seek justice while Galindo’s deal takes an unexpected turn south of the border.

episodes.name: Lahun Chan
episodes.overview: The secrets behind the death of EZ and Angel’s mother unfold.

episodes.name: Xquic
episodes.overview: An unexpected storm kicks up dust south of the border, as old family secrets bleed into familial affairs

episodes.name: Muluc
episodes.overview: Violent actions yield violent ramifications for both the MC and Galindo cartel.

episodes.name: Tohil
episodes.overview: EZ and the MC fight fire with fire, careful to not be burned in the process.

episodes.name: Kukulkan
episodes.overview: A deal is on the table for the MC but the price is paid in blood.

episodes.name: Itzam-Ye
episodes.overview: Dramatic revelations carve out different paths to vengeance.

episodes.name: Hunahpu
episodes.overview: The need for justice ignites tough decisions for the Reyes brothers and the MC.

episodes.name: Pap Struggles with the Death Angel
episodes.overview: A border shutdown squeezes the Mayan's heroin trade setting off an internal clash over the future of the club. EZ and Angel deal with the fallout of family secrets. The Galindos grow apart as Miguel loses himself in his grief and search for answers.

episodes.name: The Orneriness of Kings
episodes.overview: Now a full patch member, EZ proposes a bold plan that could change the course of the club. Adelita is freed from the U.S. government only to discover all is not as she left it with the L.O. Coco's demons lead him to a new low.

episodes.name: Overreaching Don't Pay
episodes.overview: Seeing an opportunity, Bishop sets EZ's plan into motion.

episodes.name: Our Gang's Dark Oath
episodes.overview: The M.C. scrambles to find a solution to their heroin problem. EZ digs to discover who betrayed the club.

episodes.name: Dark, Deep-Laid Plans
episodes.overview: Bishop takes a risky approach to solve the club's supply problems.

episodes.name: You Can't Pray a Lie
episodes.overview: The club seeks retribution for a recent affront.

episodes.name: What Comes of Handlin' Snakeskin
episodes.overview: Bishop enlists the help of another chapter in his move against Ramos.

episodes.name: A Mixed-up and Splendid Rescue
episodes.overview: Miguel discovers disturbing new information related to his mother’s death.

episodes.name: The House of Death Floats By
episodes.overview: The club welcomes a new member. Miguel seeks retribution on his mother’s behalf.

episodes.name: Chapter the Last, Nothing More to Write
episodes.overview: Bishop pulls the trigger on his plan to become the only king.

episodes.name: Cleansing of the Temple
episodes.overview: War descends on Santo Padre.

episodes.name: Hymn Among Ruins
episodes.overview: The club navigates a tenuous new world order.

episodes.name: Self Portrait in a Blue Bathroom
episodes.overview: In order for Santo Padre to get back in the drug trade, EZ must carry out a favor.

episodes.name: A Crow Flew By
episodes.overview: Internal strife bleeds into club business; an old enemy has found sanctuary south of the border.

episodes.name: Death of the Virgin
episodes.overview: The divided M.C. comes together in honour of their fallen brothers.

episodes.name: When I Die, I Want Your Hands on My Eyes
episodes.overview: In the wake of tragedy, the club demands answers.

episodes.name: Dialogue with the Mirror
episodes.overview: As the M.C. strikes against the Sons, EZ finds himself at an unexpected crossroads.

episodes.name: The Righteous Wrath of an Honorable Man
episodes.overview: The Mayans bring death to SOA's door step.

episodes.name: The Calling of Saint Matthew
episodes.overview: A proposed alliance promises to return the M.C. to its former glory.

episodes.name: When the Breakdown Hit at Midnight
episodes.overview: EZ ties up loose ends as the future of the club hangs in the balance. Alvarez seeks peace with a Redwood Original.

episodes.name: I Hear the Train A-Comin
episodes.overview: SONS escalate the war as EZ attempts to reclaim the pipeline.

episodes.name: Lord Help My Poor Soul
episodes.overview: EZ’s attempt to reclaim the pipeline brings danger to the club’s doorstep.

episodes.name: Do You Hear the Rain
episodes.overview: Determined to reclaim the pipeline, the M.C. begins a new trade.

episodes.name: I See the Black Light
episodes.overview: After a fatal error, the Mayans navigate the dangers of their new trade, forcing an unlikely alliance.

episodes.name: I Want Nothing but Death
episodes.overview: As the war with the Sons escalates, the two clubs square off in a fight to the death.

episodes.name: My Eyes Filled and Then Closed on the Last of Childhood Tears
episodes.overview: On the anniversary of their mother's death, EZ takes Angel on a fatal journey.

episodes.name: To Fear of Death, I Eat the Stars
episodes.overview: The M.C.’s fight to gain control of California takes a deadly twist. The Broken Saints welcome a desperate newcomer.

episodes.name: Her Blacks Crackle and Drag
episodes.overview: The MC unite for a final goodbye.

episodes.name: I Must Go in Now for the Fog Is Rising
episodes.overview: As the Sons close in on the Mayans, EZ crosses paths with a familiar stranger.

episodes.name: Slow to Bleed Fair Son
episodes.overview: The end.
